The map where it rains men! Counter terrorists to be precise...

The first from my Aperture Experiment Series!
In this universe, Aperture science simulates combats in order to study the subjects (you and the bots), each map is enclosed in a cube, where anyone who attempts to escape will certainly die! So fight for your survival and win!

First upload, not first map made!

Enjoy as a Terrorist shooting the glass below the enemy to make them fall to their death! It may sound easy, but the CT can make their way down (At least 2 ways to get to the bottom and knife them down!) and knife you unexpectedly!

Play it as intended and with a friend shoot bots down, or get as many friends as you can and put them by your side on the glass chamber, and shoot at your friends feet before they make you fall!

GAMEPLAY
The CT spawn on a chamber with glass breakable floor, with no buy zone (You have to unclick pistols or bot_allow_pistols 0 on the console so they don’t shoot at you). Terrorist spawn below and they can buy weapons (So choose freely! Buy zone is only on 2 small areas marked on the ground). Then just start breaking the glass, you can try to kill them before they hit the ground and see the ragdolls fall down, hilarity ensure. Be creative!

2 TERRORIST
30 COUNTER TERRORIST

UPDATE
Changes
1.-Now spawn with knife, no need to change anything into console, other than mp_limitteams and mp_autoteambalance
2.-HDR lighting
3.- Optimized, should run smoother compared to first release
4.- Changed to a black skybox! Now it has an abstract look to it
5.- Renamed to mg_glassfloor for nomenclature consistency

developed by Eugenio 'motanum' Roman
bugs, comments, suggestions to agent_2114@hotmail.com

Finally after endless hours of trying to get this map finished, im glad to announce the release of cp_lets_play_tf2_v1. This is a control point map (like the ones in tf2) where one team is attacking while the other defends. The attacking team must cap all 3 points in a timelimit, while the defenders must hold them off until the timer hits 0. Please do not rename the map as it will mess up the custom textures. Its cp_ prefix just in case more of these maps start appearing. But this will still be on minigames servers.
About The Map
  • Attacking/ Defending team swapper every round.
  • Seven classes to choose from.
  • 3 Control points (A, B and C).
  • Numerous teleport exit locations for engineer to set up.
  • Count down timer in skybox and at spawn.
  • Health Kits around the map.
  • Ammo Kits around the map.
  • Controllable teleport locations for engineer.
  • 4 minute round timer.
  • 4 additional minutes added to the clock once a point has been fully capped.
  • 60 second capping timer on each point.
  • 3D Skybox.
  • Custom radar map overview.
  • Tf2 like weapon strip on round win/lose.
  • And much more...
    This map requires team work and co-operation, when we was beta testing on a 30-40 slot server the map was as balanced as it probably will get. It comes down to how well your team work together and communicate with each other. If you would like to try this map visit steamgamers minigames server @ STEAMGAMERS.COM | MiniGames | *Funtastic* @ 72.26.196.164:27015

+ABOUT+ This is the third and final rendition of buses_from_hell. It has been completely remade from scratch. I hope you enjoy it! +HOW TO PLAY+ Counter-Terrorists: Survive in the arena for 90 seconds while avoiding the buses from hell! Terrorists: Climb up the towers to take control of the buses from hell! WASD to drive the bus. Left Click for powers!

"The Short Bus" - Left Click to send players and objects flying! - HIGH DAMAGE

-Added electric walls -Added more cars and objects -Added visible countdown timer -Added more dramatic T destruction sequence -Updated graphics and skybox -AND A LOT MORE! +NOTES+ I highly recommend these server CVARs: mp_limitteams 64 mp_autoteambalance 0 mp_freezetime 0 Also, the map is 3mb so use .bz2 on your server!

BUSES FROM HELL!!! Ever wonder what it would be like if you were thrown into a gladiatorial arena and forced to battle two buses from HELL?! Well, now you can experience it for yourself in the safety of your own home! This is... BUSES_FROM_HELLv2! Objectives: T's - Control the buses with your MIND and try to run over the CT's! Kill them all! CT's - Survive the onslaught of buses by ducking, diving, and dodging! Stay alive for two minutes to win! Notes: My friends and I had a blast testing this map, get about 5+ people and I guarantee you will have a good time. Start the mayhem! UPDATE 4/16/09 -Fixed the spawns -Added more CT spawns (now supports 64 player games) -Added/edited some minor geometry -Made it easier to see the CT's under the T platform -Minor graphical upgrades -Added some more props/cars. !!!!MAKE SURE YOU TURN TEAM BALANCING OFF!!!!
